OL,6,FChristie had already attempted suicide
OL,7,Fusing these taps while in West Lane
OL,8,FHospital, and spent time in intensive
OL,9,Fcare before returning to the hospital.
OL,10,FHer bathroom had those same taps
OL,11,Fagain, and in June 2019, Christie died
OL,12,Fby suicide.
OL,14,FWest Lane Hospital was closed down two
OL,15,Fmonths later after the death of
OL,16,Fanother patient, Nadia Sharif.
OL,18,FPatient X was admitted to another of
OL,19,Fthe trust's hospitals, Roseberry Park
OL,20,Fin Middlesbrough, in late 2020.
