OL,6,FHer room also had these same taps and,
OL,7,Flike Christie, she took her own life
OL,8,Fusing them.
OL,10,FThis is the first time a mental health
OL,11,Ftrust in the region has been
OL,12,Fprosecuted for the death of patients
OL,13,Funder their care, and these types of
OL,14,Fprosecutions are incredibly rare.
OL,16,FIn court today, both families gave
OL,17,Fpowerful victim impact statements.
