OL,6,FChristie's stepfather, Michael
OL,7,FHarnett, described the day Christie
OL,8,Fwent into hospital as the worst period
OL,9,Fof their ives.
OL,11,FHer mother Charlotte added: "I didn't
OL,12,Fjust lose my daughter, I lost my whole
OL,13,Ffamily and I lost myself. We are no
OL,14,Flonger the same people we were.
OL,15,FChristie really was the sunshine in
OL,16,Four lives.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/15
