OL,6,FChristie's grandmother, Casey Tremain,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Christie loved to sing and
OL,8,Fdance. She loved to watch musicals,
OL,9,Fthe Greatest Showman was her favourite.
OL,11,F"Next to singing, shopping was her
OL,12,Ffavourite past time. Shopping for prom
OL,13,Fwas great. She wanted sparkle, a lot
OL,14,Fof sparkle.
OL,16,F"Christie was a beautiful, courageous
OL,17,Fyoung woman who would always fight for
OL,18,Fthe underdog. She was like a mother
OL,19,Fhen to her siblings. She was such a
OL,20,Fwarm loving girl who could make you
OL,21,Fhappy by just being around.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/15
