OL,6,F"I promised Christie I would get her
OL,7,Fthe right help, I failed her. Seeing
OL,8,Fher in the chapel of rest was awful. I
OL,9,Ftouched her arm and expected warmth
OL,10,Fbut she was cold and grey.
OL,12,F"In my opinion she was failed on a
OL,13,Fcolossal scale. She is forever 17,
OL,14,Fdead and buried because people didn't
OL,15,Fcare for her or listen.
OL,17,F"My life will never be the same. I
OL,18,Ffeel numb all of the time and I am
OL,19,Fjust dragging myself through life.
OL,20,FThis is me now until I leave this
OL,21,Fearth.
