OL,6,F"I tell them over and over again mummy
OL,7,Fdidn't do this because she didn't love
OL,8,Fyou, she did it because she was poorly.
OL,10,F"My daughter would be proud of what
OL,11,Fthey are achieving. I am devastated
OL,12,Fshe is not here to see them. You will
OL,13,Fnever understand how hard it is to
OL,14,Ftell a child their mammy is now a star
OL,15,Fin the sky."
OL,17,FThe Trust's CEO, Brent Kilmurray, has
OL,18,Falso given a own statement, which
OL,19,Freads: "As we made clear in court
OL,20,Ftoday, we're deeply sorry for the
OL,21,Fevents that led to these tragedies.
