OL,6,F"We didn't provide the care these two
OL,7,Fpeople deserved, and the guilty pleas
OL,8,Freflect that. Of course, that's no
OL,9,Fconsolation for Patient X and
OL,10,FChristy's loved ones, for which I
OL,11,Foffer our heartfelt apologies.J"The
OL,12,FCQC has acknowledged in our latest
OL,13,Finspection that improvements have been
OL,14,Fmade since then, however today is
OL,15,Fabout being accountable and our
OL,16,Fthoughts are with the families at this
OL,17,Fincredibly difficult time."
OL,19,FThe Trust has also confirmed Mr
OL,20,FKilmurray will not be resigning.
