OL,6,FFollowing the hearing, Ann Ford,
OL,7,Fdirector of operations in the north
OL,8,Ffor the Care Quality Commission, said:
OL,9,F"These are tragic cases, and my
OL,10,Fthoughts are with both families and
OL,11,Fothers grieving for their loss.
OL,13,F"People have the right to safe care
OL,14,Fand treatment, which Christie and
OL,15,Fperson X didn't receive from Tees, Esk
OL,16,Fand Wear Valleys NHS Foundation Trust.
