OL,7,FHealth and Social Care to ask if a
OL,8,Fpublic inquiry would be commissioned
OL,9,Finto the Trust.
OL,11,FIn response, a Department of Health
OL,12,Fand Social Care spokesperson said:
OL,13,F"The safety of all patients is of
OL,14,Fvital importance, and our thoughts are
OL,15,Fwith the families and loved ones
OL,16,Fimpacted by this tragedy.
